    "description": "The Secret of Whispering is a captivating psychological horror puzzle game that immerses the player deep into the dark secrets of a long-abandoned house. Amidst a gloomy and menacing atmosphere, the player is lured by mysterious voices from the past into the property, which has stood empty for decades.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAs they explore the dilapidated rooms and hidden corridors, they gradually uncover disturbing clues that point to a tragic past. But the deeper the player delves into the secrets of the house, the more the boundaries between reality and nightmare become blurred.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWith every puzzle solved, the story becomes denser and the atmosphere more menacing, until the player finally realizes that the true danger lurks not only in the walls of the house, but also in the darkness that spreads through their own thoughts.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nExperience an intense horror adventure in which every decision counts and the fear grows with every step. Will you escape the secrets of the house, or will you be lost in the whispers of the past?",
